παρέρχομαι Subjunctive and optative from verb πάρειμι
εἶμι Indicative has future meaning. The other moods are used for present ἔρχομαι
ἔρχομαι Subjunctive and optative from verb εἶμι
ἀνώγειν with present or imperfect meaning
ἠνώγεα with present or imperfect meaning
δῐέρχομαι Subjunctive and optative from verb δίειμι
πέρσω, πέρσομαι middle in passive sense
